NAME
    Devel::Trace::More - Like Devel::Trace but with more control

SYNOPSIS
      #!/usr/bin/perl -d:Trace::More

      use Devel::Trace::More qw{ filter_on output_to };
      
  filter_on('blah');

      # or

  filter_on(qr/blah/);

      To print to a file:

  output_to('path/to/file')

DESCRIPTION
    For now look at documentation for Devel::Trace. More features to come!

SEE ALSO
    Devel::Trace

